---
title: Crumbed Chicken Dippers & Rosemary Roasted Potato Wedges with Garlic Aioli
description: We’re officially making chicken (dippers) tonight, so don’t be afraid to break out your best chicken dance! We recommend drizzling over the delicious garlic aioli, but these are called dippers so…if you need to grab ‘em and dunk ‘em, we won’t tell anyone. Promise.
